        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4014",
        "content": "He had disappeared when the sailor said to me, 'I think that was the fellow-the one that just went by.' Not wanting to arouse his suspicions, I ended the conversation with a casual remark, and then strolled away until I was out of the sailor's sight, and then hurried as fast as I could toward the engine room.",
