        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4014",
        "content": "Then, just as dawn was breaking, the infantry onslaught, participated in at some points by detachments of cavalry, began.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
